== Описание == 

Инструмент [[Image:Sketcher_JoinCurves.svg|24px]] [[Sketcher_JoinCurves/ru|Объединить кривые]] создаёт B-сплайн, соединяя два существующих [[B-Splines/ru|B-сплайна]] или другие рёбра.

<span id="Usage"></span>
== Применение ==

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
# Do one of the following:
#* Select an end point of two B-splines or other edges.
#* Select a [[Sketcher_ConstrainCoincident|coincident point]] connecting two B-splines or other edges.
# There are several ways to invoke the tool: 
#* Press the {{Button|[[Image:Sketcher_JoinCurves.svg|16px]] [[Sketcher_JoinCurves|Join curves]]}} button.
#* Select the {{MenuCommand|Sketch → Sketcher B-spline tools → [[Image:Sketcher_JoinCurves.svg|16px]] Join curves}} option from the menu.
#* {{Version|1.0}}: Right-click in the [[3D_view|3D view]] and select the {{MenuCommand|[[Image:Sketcher_JoinCurves.svg|16px]] Join curves}} option from the context menu.
</div>


